OL,3,CNHS whistleblowing: Health workers ask
OL,4,Cto join Lucy Letby inquiry
OL,6,FA group representing hundreds of
OL,7,Fhealth workers has asked to contribute
OL,8,Fto the Lucy Letby inquiry, saying
OL,9,Fthere is a need to challenge NHS
OL,10,Fculture around whistleblowing.
OL,12,FNHS Whistleblowers, a support group
OL,13,Fmade up of current and former doctors,
OL,14,Fmidwives and nurses, said workers
OL,15,Fshould able to give evidence regarding
OL,16,Fan NHS "culture detrimental to patient
OL,17,Fsafety".
