OL,3,CNHS whistleblowing: Health workers ask
OL,4,Cto join Lucy Letby inquiry
OL,6,FLetby was sentenced to 14 whole life
OL,7,Forders after she was convicted of
OL,8,Fmurdering seven babies and attempting
OL,9,Fto murder six others, with two
OL,10,Fattempts on one of her victims.
OL,12,FThe offences took place at the
OL,13,FCountess of Chester Hospital's
OL,14,Fneonatal unit, where Letby worked,
OL,15,Fbetween June 2015 and June 2016.
OL,17,FOne of the country's most senior
OL,18,Fjudges, Lady Justice Thirlwall, is
OL,19,Fleading the inquiry into how the nurse
OL,20,Fwas able to murder and how the
OL,21,Fhospital handled concerns about her.
