OL,3,CNHS whistleblowing: Health workers ask
OL,4,Cto join Lucy Letby inquiry
OL,6,FNow, NHS Whistleblowers has instructed
OL,7,FHudgell Solicitors to represent it,
OL,8,Farguing there is a need to look at
OL,9,Fproblems across the entire health
OL,10,Fservice, not just in one trust.
OL,12,FHudgell chief executive Rachel Di
OL,13,FClemente said: "This group of health
OL,14,Fprofessionals has come forward with no
OL,15,Fagenda other than making a positive
OL,16,Fchange across our health service in
OL,17,Fterms of improving patient safety.
