OL,6,FThe group said a recurring theme
OL,7,Facross NHS trusts is senior managers
OL,8,Fplacing "reputational damage
OL,9,Flimitation ahead of patient and staff
OL,10,Fsafety".
OL,12,FNHS Whistleblowers says it has more
OL,13,Fthan 1,600 members, many of whom were
OL,14,Fdismissed after facing employment
OL,15,Ftribunals, some who resigned after
OL,16,Ftheir concerns were ignored, and some
OL,17,Fwho are still working in the NHS.
