OL,6,FCathryn Watters, founder and director
OL,7,Fof NMCWatch, which represents nearly
OL,8,F600 nurses and midwives and is part of
OL,9,Fthe group, said: "Many of our group
OL,10,Fhave been whistleblowers or have
OL,11,Fraised serious concerns in their
OL,12,Fworkplace to find they are referred on
OL,13,Fspurious grounds, often with no basis
OL,14,For evidence of minor issues that could
OL,15,Fhave been dealt with at employer level.
