OL,6,F"We feel that the fitness to practise
OL,7,Fprocess is being weaponised to silence
OL,8,Fwhistleblowers and to punish those who
OL,9,Fhave continued to escalate
OL,10,Fconcerns."Healthcare regulators must
OL,11,Fget better skills to unpick this and
OL,12,Fassure further patient harm is not
OL,13,Fbeing risked in pursuit of such cases."
