OL,4,Cto join Lucy Letby inquiry
OL,6,FDr Matt Kneale, co-chairman of
OL,7,FDoctors' Association UK, which is also
OL,8,Fpart of the group, said: "NHS staff
OL,9,Fwho have bravely spoken up about
OL,10,Fpatient safety concerns or unethical
OL,11,Fpractices deserve to have their voices
OL,12,Fheard and experiences carefully
OL,13,Fexamined.
OL,15,F"By granting NHS Whistleblowers core
OL,16,Fparticipant status, the inquiry can
OL,17,Fensure it has direct access to the
OL,18,Fperspectives of those on the front
OL,19,Flines who have witnessed troubling
OL,20,Fpractices first-hand.
